    "description": "Provider config must include contract_version = 1. When the mint output format, exit code protocol, or input contracts change, the version increments. noscope must support at least the current and previous version. Without versioning, evolving the provider contract breaks existing providers silently.",
    "projectId": "9887a770-ff7d-44d4-aeeb-a9c7b2252b73",
    "sourceRefs": [],
    "statement": "noscope shall version the provider contract, requiring contract_version in provider config and supporting backward compatibility when the contract evolves",
