      "statement": "When noscope fails before spawning a child, it must use sysexits.h range: 64=usage error, 65=mint failure, 66=profile/config not found, 69=provider unavailable, 70=internal error, 77=permission denied, 78=config error. When the child ran and exited, noscope always uses the child exit code regardless of post-exit cleanup.",
      "status": "draft"
    },
