      "statement": "A profile TOML must contain one or more [[credentials]] entries. Each must specify provider (string, required), role (string, required), ttl (duration string, required). Optional: env_key (defaults to provider config). Unknown fields at top level are ignored. Unknown fields within [[credentials]] are an error. Empty credentials array is an error.",
