      ],
      "statement": "During atomic rollback of failed multi-credential minting (NS-006), revocation of already-minted credentials follows the same timeout and retry policy as signal-triggered revocation (NS-027). If rollback revocation fails, log failure with credential ID and TTL. TTL is the safety net.",
