      ],
      "statement": "Parallel credential minting must enforce a per-provider timeout (default 30 seconds, configurable). If any provider exceeds timeout, treat as mint failure triggering atomic rollback per NS-006. Total minting phase bounded by maximum per-provider timeout.",
