      ],
      "statement": "Provider config files must declare supported operations: supports_refresh (boolean, default false) and supports_revoke (boolean, default false). If supports_refresh is false, noscope must not attempt refresh and rely solely on TTL. If supports_revoke is false, skip revocation and log a warning. Mint is always required.",
