      "statement": "On provider failure, noscope must capture stderr (up to 4096 bytes, UTF-8, non-UTF-8 replaced with replacement character) and include it in error messages prefixed with provider name. On success, stderr is discarded unless --verbose. noscope must scan relayed provider stderr for token values and redact matches.",
