      "statement": "Provider refresh commands must receive the current token via NOSCOPE_TOKEN, current token ID via NOSCOPE_TOKEN_ID, and requested TTL via NOSCOPE_TTL environment variables. Output must follow the same JSON contract as mint (NS-009). If token value unchanged in response, noscope treats it as lease renewal.",
