      "statement": "Provider revoke commands must receive the token value via the NOSCOPE_TOKEN environment variable and token ID (if available) via NOSCOPE_TOKEN_ID. Token values must never be passed as command-line arguments. Revoke commands must exit 0 for already-revoked tokens (NS-014 idempotency).",
