      "statement": "noscope must enforce a timeout on all provider command executions (default 30 seconds, configurable). If a provider exceeds the timeout, noscope sends SIGTERM, waits 5 seconds, then SIGKILL, and treats the result as exit code 4 (provider unavailable).",
