      "statement": "Template variables ({role}, {ttl}) must be substituted as single arguments in an argv array, never interpolated into a shell string. noscope must never pass template values through a shell interpreter. Role values must be validated against a safe pattern: alphanumeric, hyphens, underscores, dots only. Values containing shell metacharacters must be rejected.",
